      "bullets": [
        "Reaction is a Go-based, lightweight alternative to Fail2ban that scans logs and standard outputs to trigger security actions.",
        "It integrates with systemd-journald and files, triggering custom mitigation actions via iptables, nftables, or arbitrary shell commands.",
        "The tool provides a modern, low-footprint, single-binary daemon for host-based intrusion prevention and automated pattern-matching response."
      ]
