      "bullets": [
        "Internal package structures (npm, NuGet, PyPI) naturally mirror organizational silos, reflecting Conway's Law in artifact dependency graphs.",
        "Over-segmented registries create complex dependency hell, requiring clear team ownership boundaries in Artifactory, Nexus, or GitHub Packages.",
        "Mitigate org-chart-induced integration bottlenecks using monorepos or automated dependency updates with tools like Dependabot or Renovate."
      ]
